` FSx for ONTAP Forensic Investigation — Step 2: All Activity
` Full event stream for a user/time window, sorted newest first.
` Token: $user$ (Windows/AD username, e.g., CORP\jdoe)

index=fsxn_audit user="$user$"
| sort - _time
| table _time, user, operation, path, client_ip, result, svm, volume
| rename _time AS "Timestamp", user AS "User", operation AS "Operation",
         path AS "File Path", client_ip AS "Client IP", result AS "Result",
         svm AS "SVM", volume AS "Volume"
